{"tid":707820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一定一定要珍惜剩低同父母相處既時間","createTime":"2018-06-19T02:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:48:12.000Z","uid":66436,"like":89,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8842341ff80b6e44e5467f5a5686f9e301d09ca2","tid":707820,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"每當父母哦你問你既時候 我諗好多人都試過嫌煩 然後務求一兩句內hea覆end左個topic佢 或者甚至無視<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地有冇試過 每當係兩登或者網上總會睇到啲勸世文講類似既野<br />\n你可能會一笑置之 又或者感觸幾秒 然後用半秒反省再用多半秒下決心要對屋企人好啲<br />\n但無論你係邊種都好 99.87%情況下再過多幾十個半秒<br />\n你就會拋低左當初既決心 <br />\n然後周而復始繼續落去<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地有冇留意到過<br />\n不知不覺間 父母開始多左白髮<br />\n不知不覺間 對比起牆上或者櫃入面既合照 原來佢地已經蒼老左好多<br />\n不知不覺間 係街到一齊行既時候 行下行下發現佢地比舊時行左慢好多<br />\n<br />\n雖然好肉麻 但每當諗到呢到 我都會忍唔住攬住屋企人講聲我愛你 <br />\n雖然真係好骨痺 但我覺得如果我唔講出口 遲啲一定會後悔<br />\n<br />\n因為我一直覺得好多時永遠都係得屋企人 永遠都只求付出不求回報 永遠都眼裡只得你 永遠唔洗怕比人出賣<br />\n<br />\n永遠唔洗擔心對方講既每一句係咪謊言<br />\n<br />\n歌都有得唱<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多好玩的東西 早晚會放低<br />\n從前並肩的好兄弟 可會撐到底<br />\n愛侶愛到一個地步便另覓安慰<br />\n枉當初苦苦送禮 最艷的花卉 最後化爛泥</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再親密既伴侶再親密既朋友 絕大部份既佢地無一例都會成為生命中既過客 時間耐左可能連樣都開始諗唔起<br />\n但父母永遠都會係你身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次聽呢三首歌 我都會忍唔住流馬淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一首講老豆 一首講老母 一首講自己<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BfwbO0f1R8o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBfwbO0f1R8o&d=R0oyRw0%2F7CAxgVAVebxmzG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=34d33709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BfwbO0f1R8o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FViqNhuXgROc&d=R0oyRw0%2F7CAxgVAVebxmzG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=51e05c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y6hQHdLZa8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy6hQHdLZa8E&d=R0oyRw0%2F7CAxgVAVebxmzG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ec7a5e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y6hQHdLZa8E</a><br />\n<br />\nPS 仆街父母請手下留情別駁嘴"},{"pid":"fdf7072f73579d507f90e0b4318c3bf127e90a9f","tid":707820,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c736d26d8b5f326830c802fe66a88106ef6b145c","tid":707820,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf7072f73579d507f90e0b4318c3bf127e90a9f","tid":707820,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"毒撚Kai post沒人理 柒到找loan捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27273442493cac7f0b98a459d7654e4a8931c5c9","tid":707820,"uid":1703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"岩啊 但諗到要嫁人去人地屋企服侍人地父母<br />\n不如都係唔好嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028cfc45d42d5d196fc257879e6e3981bbe1e929","tid":707820,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20a9f6df2db18f38c54b9f8724beac327158ddef","tid":707820,"uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27273442493cac7f0b98a459d7654e4a8931c5c9","tid":707820,"uid":1703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"岩啊 但諗到要嫁人去人地屋企服侍人地父母<br />\n不如都係唔好嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T0